- To install new language server
    - `:LspInstall <name>`
    - `:LspInstallInfo` -> For more info and stuff
+ After installing language server, set it up in `user/lua/lsp/settings`

+ Fuzzy searching
    - `:Telescope find_files` `Ctrl f`
    - Also supprots language server
    - `:Telescope lsp_*`

+ Install syntax hilighting (Tree sitters)
    - `:TSInstall <name>`
	- `:TSHighlightCaptureUnderCursor` => Good for color scheme development
	- `:TSPlayground` => :D

+ Completion
    - `Ctrl-Space` => Normal Completion
    - `Ctrl-K` => Function param help

+ Comments
    - gcc => Single line 
    - Select and gc -> visual block

+ Formatting
    - `:Format`

+ Nvim tree
    - `:NvimTreeToggle`
    - new file `a`
    - delete file `d`
    - rename `r`

+ Terminal
    - `Ctrl \`
	- `:LazyGit` => `<leader>`g
	- NUM + `Ctrl \` -> horizontal terminal number 
	- NUM `<leader>t`  -> same as above but vertical
	- `<leader>`T => Toggles all terminals hide or open


+ Increase window size
    - `Ctrl UP`
    - `Ctrl Down`

+ Move windows
    - `Ctrl Alt j/k/l/h`

+ Open tree
	- `Ctrl t` -> toggles nvimtree

+ Moving between buffers
	- `L` `(Shift + l)` -> to right
	- `H` `(Shift + h)` -> to left
	- `D` `(Shift + D)` -> :bd
